response.original_title: Batman and the Oscar Night interrogation
response.overview: In this Batman movie, shot only within 3 hours, without a script and edited in only a week....  Batman and his (so called) pal, Commissioner James Gordan, interrogate the Joker for his craziest crime yet... peeing on a bus. But what starts as an absurd accusation soon escalates into a conspiracy more twisted than they could have ever predicted.
response.tagline: A Batman movie, without prep time.
response.title: Batman and the Oscar Night interrogation
